Automatic daily comics grabber for Kindle, with modules support.

INSTALL
 * Change your Kindle address in comics.php
 * Modify modules, you want to receive in comics.php
 * Change sender email in email.class.php - You must allow this address in you Amazon account
 * ^^ All these steps are marked as @BEFORE-FIRST-START, use grep to find them all
 * Download kindlegen from Amazon site and put kindlegen file in same directory, as comics.php

